    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="初识列表"><a href="#初识列表" class="headerlink" title="初识列表"></a>初识列表</h1><p>如果你要列出家庭成员列表，你可能会这样写：</p><p><img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/9107736-7ea3cafe6af8f78c.jpeg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/328" alt=""></p><p>我们用Python来实现</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">family_numbers = [<span class="string">"Mom"</span>, <span class="string">"Dad"</span>, <span class="string">"Allen"</span>]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>如果让你列出你的幸运数字，你可能会这样写：</p><p><img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/9107736-9f33541efa40945b.jpeg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/223" alt=""></p><p>我们用Python来实现</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">lucky_numbers = [<span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">7</span>, <span class="number">14</span>, <span class="number">26</span>, <span class="number">30</span>]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><a id="more"></a><h2 id="创建列表、向列表中添加元素"><a href="#创建列表、向列表中添加元素" class="headerlink" title="创建列表、向列表中添加元素"></a>创建列表、向列表中添加元素</h2><p>创建一个空列表：</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">li = []</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>向列表中添加元素</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">li.append(<span class="number">123</span>)</span><br><span class="line">li.append(<span class="string">"python"</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/9107736-005f42bdcab7febd.jpeg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/402" alt=""></p><p>注：向列表中添加元素之前首先要创建一个列表，既可以是空列表也可以是非空列表。<br>我们可以把列表看成是一个容器。</p><p><img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/9107736-39f251613f605981.jpeg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/533" alt=""></p><p>列表长度</p><p><img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/9107736-0d1d725ebce618e6.jpeg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/443" alt=""></p><p>列表求和</p><p><img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/9107736-18e140a7932822b4.jpeg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/432" alt=""></p><p>习题：输入班级学生的Python期末考试分数，遇到quit停止输入，并将分数保存到列表中，最后计算出班级平均分。</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">score = input(<span class="string">"Please input score: "</span>)</span><br><span class="line">score_list = []</span><br><span class="line">num = <span class="number">0</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">while</span> score != <span class="string">"quit"</span>:</span><br><span class="line">    num += <span class="number">1</span></span><br><span class="line">    score_list.append(int(score))</span><br><span class="line">    score = input(<span class="string">"Please input score: "</span>)</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">print(<span class="string">"score_list = "</span>, score_list)</span><br><span class="line">print(<span class="string">"average score = "</span>, sum(score_list) / len(score_list))</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="列表的索引"><a href="#列表的索引" class="headerlink" title="列表的索引"></a>列表的索引</h2><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">print(li[<span class="number">0</span>])</span><br><span class="line">print(li[<span class="number">1</span>])</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>注：列表的索引从0开始。</p><h2 id="列表的分片"><a href="#列表的分片" class="headerlink" title="列表的分片"></a>列表的分片</h2><p>我们使用索引一次从列表中获取多个元素就叫做列表的分片。</p><p><img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/9107736-a7c2c463d634d73e.jpeg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/469" alt=""></p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">li = [<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>, <span class="number">5</span>, <span class="number">6</span>]</span><br><span class="line">print(li[<span class="number">1</span>: <span class="number">3</span>])</span><br><span class="line">print(li[ : <span class="number">4</span>])</span><br><span class="line">print(li[<span class="number">2</span>: ])</span><br><span class="line">print(li[ : ])</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/9107736-555af4ff8a06ea85.jpeg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/669" alt=""></p><p>习题：输入一个列表，逆序输出（例：a = [1, 2, 3, 4, 5, 6], 得到b = [6, 5, 4, 3 ,2, 1]）</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">a = [<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>, <span class="number">5</span>, <span class="number">6</span>]</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">b = []</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"><span class="keyword">for</span> i <span class="keyword">in</span> range(len(a)):</span><br><span class="line">    b.append(a[len(a) - i - <span class="number">1</span>])</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">print(b)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h2 id="修改元素"><a href="#修改元素" class="headerlink" title="修改元素"></a>修改元素</h2><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">li = [<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="number">2</span>, <span class="number">3</span>, <span class="number">4</span>, <span class="number">5</span>, <span class="number">6</span>]</span><br><span class="line">li[<span class="number">0</span>] = <span class="string">"Allen"</span></span><br><span class="line">li[<span class="number">3</span>] = <span class="number">99</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/9107736-3f0f290f0526fa1e.jpeg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/507" alt=""></p><h2 id="扩展列表extend"><a href="#扩展列表extend" class="headerlink" title="扩展列表extend()"></a>扩展列表extend()</h2><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">li = [<span class="string">'a'</span>, <span class="string">'b'</span>, <span class="string">'c'</span>]</span><br><span class="line">li.extend([<span class="string">'d'</span>, <span class="string">'e'</span>, <span class="string">'f'</span>])</span><br><span class="line">li.append([<span class="string">'g'</span>, <span class="string">'h'</span>])</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/9107736-8251553d936feff4.jpeg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/700" alt=""></p><p>注：区分append()和extend()</p><h2 id="插入一个元素insert"><a href="#插入一个元素insert" class="headerlink" title="插入一个元素insert()"></a>插入一个元素insert()</h2><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">li = [<span class="string">'a'</span>, <span class="string">'b'</span>, <span class="string">'c'</span>] </span><br><span class="line">li.insert(<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="string">'d'</span>) </span><br><span class="line">li.insert(<span class="number">1</span>, <span class="string">'e'</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/9107736-bd4ea2621b37cc82.jpeg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/495" alt=""></p><h2 id="删除元素"><a href="#删除元素" class="headerlink" title="删除元素"></a>删除元素</h2><h3 id="remove-删除元素"><a href="#remove-删除元素" class="headerlink" title="remove()删除元素"></a>remove()删除元素</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">li = [<span class="string">'a'</span>, <span class="string">'b'</span>, <span class="string">'c'</span>, <span class="string">'d'</span>, <span class="string">'e'</span>, <span class="string">'f'</span>]</span><br><span class="line">li.remove(<span class="string">'d'</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="del-删除"><a href="#del-删除" class="headerlink" title="del 删除"></a>del 删除</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="keyword">del</span> li[<span class="number">3</span>]</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><h3 id="pop-删除元素"><a href="#pop-删除元素" class="headerlink" title="pop()删除元素"></a>pop()删除元素</h3><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">li.pop()</span><br><span class="line">li.pop(<span class="number">1</span>)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/9107736-cb803c3e8bf290b7.jpeg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/633" alt=""></p><h2 id="搜索列表"><a href="#搜索列表" class="headerlink" title="搜索列表"></a>搜索列表</h2><p><img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/9107736-c7f2cbc1bad44220.jpeg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/521" alt=""></p><h2 id="查找索引index"><a href="#查找索引index" class="headerlink" title="查找索引index()"></a>查找索引index()</h2><p><img src="https://upload-images.jianshu.io/upload_images/9107736-ec436143932df2cb.jpeg?imageMogr2/auto-orient/strip%7CimageView2/2/w/484" alt=""></p><h2 id="列表排序"><a href="#列表排序" class="headerlink" title="列表排序"></a>列表排序</h2><h3 id="sort-排序"><a href="#sort-排序" class="headerlink" title="sort()排序"></a>sort()排序</h3><p>顺序排序</p><figure class="highlight python"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br><span class="line">6</span><br><span class="line">7</span><br><span class="line">8</span><br><span class="line">9</span><br><span class="line">10</span><br><span class="line">11</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">letters = [<span class="string">'d'</span>, <span class="string">'a'</span>, <span class="string">'e'</span>, <span class="string">'c'</span>, <span class="string">'b'</span>]</span><br><span class="line">letters.sort()</span><br><span class="line">print(letters)</span><br><span class="line">``` </span><br><span class="line"> </span><br><span class="line">逆序排序</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">```python</span><br><span class="line">letters = [<span class="string">'d'</span>, <span class="string">'a'</span>, <span class="string">'e'</span>, <span class="string">'c'</span>, <span class="string">'b'</span>]</span><br><span class="line">letters.sort(reverse=<span class="keyword">True</span>)</span><br><span class="line">print(letters)</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
